 |year=1935
 |id={{LCCN|35|0|19093}}
}}</ref>、{{le|振荡宇宙|cyclic model}}（最早由弗里德曼提出，后来的主要推广者是[[阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦|阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦]]和[[理查德·托尔曼|理查德·托尔曼]]<ref>{{cite book|title=Relativity, Thermodynamics, and Cosmology|url=https://archive.org/details/dli.ernet.288495|last=Tolman|first=R.C.|publisher=Clarendon Press|year=1934|location=Oxford（UK）|id={{LCCN|34|0|32023}}}}

: Reissued (1987). New York (NY): Dover Publications ISBN 978-0-486-65383-9.
</ref>、[[弗里茨·兹威基|弗里茨·兹威基]]的{{le|衰减光子假说|tired light hypothesis}}<ref>{{cite journal
 |last=Zwicky
 |first=F.
